omad legally<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#benefits\">Benefits of the lifestyle<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"prep\">Preparations &#x2013; 5 Steps to take Now<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It is a big, and sometimes, scary step to become a digital nomad. Preparing well helps you to better succeed in your goals, and avoid any unnecessary problems.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125241\/beautiful-waterfall-route-bali-sekumpul.jpg\" alt=\"beautiful waterfall route bali sekumpul\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"309\" alt=\"beautiful waterfall route bali sekumpul\" class=\"wp-image-18226 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125241\/beautiful-waterfall-route-bali-sekumpul.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125241\/beautiful-waterfall-route-bali-sekumpul-300x206.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125241\/beautiful-waterfall-route-bali-sekumpul-600x412.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125241\/beautiful-waterfall-route-bali-sekumpul-800x549.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125241\/beautiful-waterfall-route-bali-sekumpul-1080x741.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125241\/beautiful-waterfall-route-bali-sekumpul-450x309.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125241\/beautiful-waterfall-route-bali-sekumpul-1536x1054.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125241\/beautiful-waterfall-route-bali-se