>\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/how-to-make-money-online\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Complete guide on how to make money online<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4>Tips to reduce spending<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#x2019;s an amazing feeling to travel with money in your pockets and no responsibilities at home! The first fairly easy step to do this is to reduce spending. For instance:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Instead of eating out, cook at home. This can be much healthier, inspires creativity, and is loads cheaper!<\/li><li>Sell some of your unwanted things. If you&#x2019;re traveling long-term, you might be able to sell your furniture, unwanted clothing, or maybe even your car.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114826\/jeep-sri-lanka.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"311\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-32399 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114826\/jeep-sri-lanka.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114826\/jeep-sri-lanka-300x207.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114826\/jeep-sri-lanka-600x414.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-con