 memberships or bills. For example your mobile phone contract or subscriptions to apps. This is an easy way to reduce outgoings.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142518\/start-a-travel-blog-social-buttons.jpg\" alt=\"start a travel blog social buttons\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"start a travel blog social buttons\" class=\"wp-image-12019 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142518\/start-a-travel-blog-social-buttons.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142518\/start-a-travel-blog-social-buttons-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142518\/start-a-travel-blog-social-buttons-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142518\/start-a-travel-blog-social-buttons-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142518\/start-a-travel-blog-social-buttons-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142518\/start-a-travel-blog-social-buttons-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142518\/start-a-travel-blog-social-buttons-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142518\/start-a-travel-blog-social-buttons-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142518\/start-a-travel-blog-social-buttons-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142518\/start-a-travel-blog-social-buttons-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142518\/start-a