al adaptors<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>This is an adaptor that works in most countries in the world. It&#x2019;s an absolute must-have, and it will save you from having problems charging your devices, for example, during a layover. (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/universal-travel-adapter\/\">Get a travel adapter here<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Learn: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/backup-photos-traveling\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">How to back-up photos while traveling<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114718\/Digital-Nomad-universal-adapter.jpg\" alt=\"Digital Nomad universal adapter\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"Digital Nomad universal adapter\" class=\"wp-image-32869 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114718\/Digital-Nomad-universal-adapter.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114718\/Digital-Nomad-universal-adapter-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114718\/Digital-Nomad-universal-adapter-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114718\/Digital-No