ourhair.com\/tips\/travel-insurance\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">find the right travel insurance<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114816\/best-work-cafe-556x810.jpg\" alt=\"best work cafe\"><\/noscript><img width=\"232\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best work cafe\" class=\"wp-image-32410 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 556px) 100vw, 556px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114816\/best-work-cafe-556x810.jpg 556w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114816\/best-work-cafe-300x437.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114816\/best-work-cafe-600x875.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114816\/best-work-cafe-412x600.jpg 412w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114816\/best-work-cafe-232x338.jpg 232w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114816\/best-work-cafe-1054x1536.jpg 1054w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114816\/best-work-cafe-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114816\/best-work-cafe-112x163.jpg 112w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114816\/best-work-cafe-123x180.jpg 123w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114816\/best-work-cafe-527x768.jpg 527w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114816\/best-work-cafe-702x1024.jpg 702w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114816\/best-work-cafe-741x1080.jpg 741w, h