ountries. But there&#x2019;s an incredible solution named <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transferwise\/\" target=\"_blank\">Wise Borderless<\/a>. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114705\/How-to-Become-Digital-Nomad-transferwise.jpg\" alt=\"How to Become Digital Nomad transferwise\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"How to Become Digital Nomad transferwise\" class=\"wp-image-32873 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114705\/How-to-Become-Digital-Nomad-transferwise.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114705\/How-to-Become-Digital-Nomad-transferwise-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114705\/How-to-Become-Digital-Nomad-transferwise-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114705\/How-to-Become-Digital-Nomad-transferwise-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114705\/How-to-Become-Digital-Nomad-transferwise-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114705\/How-to-Become-Digital-Nomad-transferwise-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114705\/How-to-Become-Digital-Nomad-transferwise-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114705\/How-to-Become-Digital-Nomad-transferwise-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114705\/How-to-Become-Digital-Nomad-transferwise-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114705\/How-to-