><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"legal\">Be a digital nomad legally<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Working as a digital nomad may mean working remotely for a company or being self-employed\/freelance. Either way, it&#x2019;s good to work out what the legalities are. For example, which country are you spending the most time in? This might affect where you pay your taxes. You will also need to apply for a visa in the various countries that you visit. Make sure to check whether you need a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/get-visa\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">tourist visa or work visa<\/a> depending on your situation. Last but not least, always make sure to have insurance!<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Here&#x2019;s how to:<\/strong>&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-insurance\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">find the right travel insurance<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"benefits\">The Benefits&#xA0;of the Digital Nomad Lifestyle<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The positives of being a digital nomad are endless:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Travel<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Travel as much or as little as you&#x2019;d like, while still earning money. This can help you to get to know new cultures or even learn a new language!<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3><strong>Freedom<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Not being tied to a specific place, or office creates the freedom to choose from any number of incredible locations. The blissful beaches of <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/bali\/\" target=\"_blank\">Bali<\/a> this week? The heavenly islands of <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/thailand\/\" target=\"_blank\">Thailand<\/a> next? It&#x2019;s all possible! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114845\/safari-elephants-562x810.jpg\" alt=\"safari elephants\"><\/noscript><img width=\"234\" height=\"338\" alt=\"safari elephants\" class=\"wp-image-32389 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114845\/safari-elephants-562x810.jpg 562w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114845\/safari-elephants-300x432.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114845\/safari-elephants-600x865.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114845\/safari-elephants-416x600.jpg 416w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114845\/safari-elephants-234x338.jpg 234w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114845\/safari-elephants-1066x1536.jpg 1066w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114845\/safari-elephants-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23114845\/safari-elephants-113x163.jpg